revision.text:
'''Afrig''' (died 4th-century) was the founder of the [[Afrighids|Afrighid dynasty]] of [[Khwarazm]]. He is said to have built a fortress known as Fil or Fir near his capital in [[Beruniy|Kath]]. Not much more is known about him; he was later succeeded by his son [[Bagra of Khwarazm|Bagra]].

