'''Tjilpa''' is the name given to a [[Quoll|marsupial cat]] amongst the Northern [[Aranda people|Aranda]] language group of [[Australian Aboriginal]] people.  There are many Dreamtime stories of tribes of ancestral '''Tjilpa'''-men, who had a significant mythological role.  The geographical range of these stories includes Aranda, [[Anmatyerre]], [[Kaytetye]], [[Ngalia]], [[Warlpiri people|Ilpara]] and [[Kukatja]] lands.

